    "66 Polycomputing emphasizes both, the read side of the interaction (where agents perceive and interpret others' activity in whatever way they want) and the write side of the interaction (where agents use this information to optimally direct other systems' behavior in ways that bring adaptive benefit to them).Figure 2:2Figure 2: Remodeling of a transplanted tail into a limb-like structure in a salamander.",
